== prompt 9 :: unit=example/math_helpers.is_even+example/math_helpers.is_odd :: pass=summary ==
You are analyzing a Python function to create a summary of its behavior.


## Functions (mutually recursive group)

```
def is_even(n: int) -> bool:
    """Mutual recursion: delegates to is_odd."""
    if n == 0:
        return True
    return is_odd(n - 1)
```

```
def is_odd(n: int) -> bool:
    """Mutual recursion: delegates to is_even."""
    if n == 0:
        return False
    return is_even(n - 1)
```


