## Receiver Type: type Counter
Counter accumulates a running total.

```
class Counter:
    """Counter accumulates a running total."""

    def __init__(self) -> None:
        """Creates a zeroed counter."""
        self.n: int = 0

    def bump(self) -> int:
        """Increments by one, returns the new value."""
        self.n = add(self.n, 1)
        return self.n

    def value(self) -> int:
        """Returns the current value."""
        return self.n
